I can't afford two bedrooms.

20
00:02:17,453 --> 00:02:18,393
How 'bout you, Dahlia?

21
00:02:18,395 --> 00:02:20,263
We need to know what your
situation is gonna be.

22
00:02:20,264 --> 00:02:23,208
