her 5th birthday.

33
00:02:43,438 --> 00:02:45,272
- No. No, I didn't.
- No?

34
00:02:45,273 --> 00:02:49,318
No, I didn't. The plane was stuck
on the tarmac, and we didn't have a gate.

35
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:52,446
