104
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:08,509
And I think they're replacing
all the doors, if I'm not mistaken.

105
00:07:08,511 --> 00:07:09,786
It'll make it a lot brighter.

106
00:07:09,787 --> 00:07:12,581
This is Mr. Veeck.
