178
00:11:07,733 --> 00:11:10,902
Yeah, that's the foyer closet.

179
00:11:10,903 --> 00:11:13,174
The bathroom's
pretty self-explanatory.

180
00:11:13,176 --> 00:11:15,615
It's in decent shape.
